        "TileImage": "$($repository ea42e21d-791c-4d70-b8f6-f2e26edbfe37).Image",
        "Description": "Welcome to New York, 47.\r\rOur clients today are Lewis Thomas and Logan Jackson, each of whom is targeting the other.\r\rAs Milton Fitzpatrick is known to be one of the most cutthroat banks in the industry, potential employees are constantly looking for any leg up on current employees so that they can replace them. Mr. Thomas seeks to cut out the middleman and simply eliminate Mr. Jackson.\r\rMr. Jackson, however, knows of Mr. Thomas&apos; ambition, and has also  hired us to eliminate him.\r\rGood luck, 47.",
